snippet.title: TRIANGLE STRATEGY - Character & Story Trailer #1: Roland Glenbrook - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Learn about Roland, the Prince of Glenbrook, and the choices and characters you'll be faced with in the first character and story trailer for TRIANGLE STRATEGY. Test the weight of your convictions in this upcoming turn-based strategy RPG from Square Enix. The decisions you make determines who joins you, will impact the path the story takes and ultimately, its outcome. Who will rise and who will fall?

#TriangleStrategy #NintendoSwitch 

Learn More! https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/triangle-strategy-switch/
